snippet.title: Neon Aileron Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Neon Aileron is a retro-style shooter where enemies spawn to the beat of the music.

For more information, check out the Neon Aileron website or Steam page:
http://neonaileron.com/
https://store.steampowered.com/app/745430/Neon_Aileron/

For more trailers and game updates, follow us on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/SaturdayDevelop

Thanks to Von Hertzog for the use of the song "Interplanetary": http://vonhertzog.com
